{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "15.0",
      "line_index": 15,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3dc2c13f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う゛……！？　ううう……ぐううっ……！！　身体が……あう……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "749efc89",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "部屋に戻ろうとしていると、突然動悸が激しくなる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.0",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9a43715",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それと同時に身体が焼かれるように熱くなり、全身から汗が噴き出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.0",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "45ea1eb0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "な、なんだ、これ……胸が、苦しい……！　ふ、ふっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.0",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "49c73cb2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "真っ直ぐ歩くこともできなくなり、上体がふらふらし始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.0",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b7766c9f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでもどうにか部屋に戻ろうと、壁に手を付きながら歩く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8874446d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょ、ちょっと！？　あんた大丈夫！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.0",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bd1e180",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "聞き慣れた幼馴染の声が背後から聞こえ、その声に振り向く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "37.0",
      "line_index": 37,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9382e129",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハ、ル……？　うあ、あああああっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4449b753",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしコハルの顔を見た瞬間、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "41.0",
      "line_index": 41,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "13470bfe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらに動悸が激しくなり耐え切れず思わず叫ぶ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5726a864",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "な、何？　何なの！？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.2",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5726a864",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょっと！　し、しっかりして！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b7616b27",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フラフラの俺の身体を支えようと、抱きつくコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "47.0",
      "line_index": 47,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "36d6bf15",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その瞬間頭の中で何かが弾け、俺の意識が途切れてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.0",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf0a9243",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょっと本当に何なの？　身体すごく熱くて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.3",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "bf0a9243",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "汗びっしょりじゃない！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.5",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 5,
      "line_hash": "bf0a9243",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "とりあえず部屋に戻って休んだ方がいいわよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "55.0",
      "line_index": 55,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1b875e5",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ほら、行くわよ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e005ca53",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "──きゃぁぁっ！？　な、ななっ、何っ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.2",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e005ca53",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "何いきなり抱きかかえて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.4",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "e005ca53",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょ、ちょっと！？　どこ行くつもり！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.0",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2b71aa14",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "──あううっ！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.3",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "2b71aa14",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "な、何なのよ、いきなりベッドに投げ捨てて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.5",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 5,
      "line_hash": "2b71aa14",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ヒドイじゃない！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "76.0",
      "line_index": 76,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "15a723b9",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うう゛！　ふーっ！　ふっ！　お、おんな……めす、メスぅぅ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f396e666",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "な、何？　やだ、ちょっとこっちこないで……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.4",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "f396e666",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "い、いやぁぁぁぁっ！！　服脱がさないでぇ！！　やめてよぉぉぉ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.0",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ab893192",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ふーっ！　ふーっ！　おんなおんなおんな……！！　おんなぁっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "88.0",
      "line_index": 88,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ed7de2aa",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "な、なんで……もしかして、国宝のせい？　それで暴走しちゃってるの！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "88.2",
      "line_index": 88,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ed7de2aa",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "きゃぁぁっ！！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "88.4",
      "line_index": 88,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "ed7de2aa",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うう……こんな乱暴にぃ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.0",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4418dea9",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "で、でも国宝のせいなら……あんたが悪いわけじゃない……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.4",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "4418dea9",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そ、それなら……せめて、やさしく……して……お願い……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.0",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a36f3b17",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──ううっ！？　ぐ、う、うあ、あ……ううう……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.0",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "94ba7626",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "こ、今度は何？　だ、大丈夫？　ねぇ、しっかりして……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.0",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fc7547d6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コ、ハル……う、ううう……！！　コハル……コハル……うう……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "efd1da92",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルの『やさしくして』の声が脳内に響き、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.2",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "efd1da92",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぷつりと途切れていた意識が急に戻り始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.0",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "13f9b611",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "徐々に視界が開け、あられもない幼馴染の姿に意識が一気に回復する。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.0",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "72dcc195",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハル……！？　こ、これ……俺もしかしてコハルに……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.0",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fb2b5ed7",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "意識戻った……の？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.3",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "fb2b5ed7",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "よ、よかったぁ……元に戻った……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "118.0",
      "line_index": 118,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8ea9dbea",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "瞳に大粒の涙が溢れ、声を押し殺して泣くコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.0",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "61fff65d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなコハルにいたたまれなくなり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.2",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "61fff65d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルから離れようとする。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "335f612d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかし──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "125.0",
      "line_index": 125,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "95c90306",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "──待って！　その……あんたの、大きいまま……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.0",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "96002e4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは俺の手を掴み、そして下半身をじっと見つめる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.0",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ac452d3f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の肉棒は限界を超え勃起しており、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.2",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ac452d3f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "痛みを覚えるほど硬くなってしまっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.0",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "39d295b9",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あたし、あんたになら……その、犯されてもいいって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.3",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "39d295b9",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "暴走されても受け入れようって、そう思ってて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e334fa70",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "だからあんたが苦しいなら……また暴走しちゃうかもしれないなら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.0",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "88c2b3cc",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あたしで発散して……あんたなら全然構わないから……だから……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.0",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b42211ec",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハル……ごめん……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.0",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fb085f4e",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ああ……本当にシちゃうんだね……あたし達……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.0",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a63794e8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……でも本当に……その、いいのか……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ef76601a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "構わないよ……♥　だって、あんたのこと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.2",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ef76601a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ずっとずっと昔から大好きだったから……♥　だから……いいの♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.0",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ee172950",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハル……ありがとう……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.0",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f54ee85b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "お礼なんて……で、でもあんたの、その、すごいわね……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.2",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f54ee85b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "血管が浮き出て……こんなの挿っちゃうんだ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.4",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "f54ee85b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ていうか、本当に挿るの……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.0",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7b18ee95",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "わかんない……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.2",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7b18ee95",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "でも今コハルと一つになりたくてたまらなくなってる……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.4",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "7b18ee95",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "苦しいかもしれないけど、受け入れてくれると嬉しい……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.0",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d8667093",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルにそう告げると、限界まで反り返っていた肉棒を",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.2",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d8667093",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルの膣穴に押し当てる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.0",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d111c5c8",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うあ……直に触れるとやっぱりすごく大きいかも……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.0",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "edb4dafc",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょっと待って……！！　これ無理かも！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.2",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "edb4dafc",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "いったんタイム！！少しだけ心の準備させて……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.0",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f20aa2a2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは俺を静止させようと叫ぶ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.0",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e20c09a8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしコハルの可愛らしい裸体を目の前にして止まることもできず、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.2",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e20c09a8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "興奮に任せるままに肉棒を一気に押し込んだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.0",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fb3c618c",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "はうっ！♥　うあ、んぅぅぅ！♥　んはぁぁぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.0",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e75b1d26",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "亀頭の先端を強引に押し込むと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.2",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e75b1d26",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "滑り込むように肉棒が膣中に納まる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.0",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6e05483",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒を締め付けるように膣壁が蠢き、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.2",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6e05483",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その気持ち良さに腰が震える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
